                "content": "Conjuncturele werkloosheid",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><strong><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">Conjuncturele werkloosheid</span></strong> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">(<span>vraagkant</span> van de economie) = te weinig vraag naar producten van</span></p>\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n<li> \n<ul type=\"circle\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">consumenten (C),</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"font-size-10pt\"> Bedrijven (I),</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">Overheid (O) of</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span class=\"font-size-10pt\">Buitenland (E)<span> </span></span></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n"
